      "side": 1,
      "message": "So IIUC, we\u0027re downloading SVGs from three places:\n1. SVGs listed in tools/svg/svgs.txt via svg_downloader\n2. SVGs listed in tools/svg/parse_svgs.txt via svg_downloader\n3. Everything in gs://skia-svgs/skbug4713/\n\nThey all become part of the same asset.  Why do they need to be in different places?",
